<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="encounter-vt">encounter <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'kaʊntə(r)/    美 /ɪn'kaʊntər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-meet-with-come-across">1.★ <strong>遇到 (问题等) (meet with)；偶然碰到 (某人) (come across)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>encounter an old friend
偶然遇到一位老朋友</p></div></div>